            <sect2>
                <title>Arms and Armour</title>

                <para>
                    The <e>Dark Ages</e> pre-date the use of plate armour,
                    and most warriors wear some form of <e>mail</e> armour.
                    Shields are common, and are usually used in combination
                    with swords or spears.
                </para>

